-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+myapp+%28ID%3A+285523%29","followersCount":4173,"postsCount":1212},{"id":"144","slug":"action-games","name":"Action Games","description":"Do you want your games to feel like they were created by Michael Bay? Check out these heart-pumping titles if you're a fan of cinematic scenes and over-the-top action.","image":"https://ph-files.imgix.net/d6efdccc-2481-45b5-9854-a146e982b615.gif?auto=format","url":"https://www.producthunt.com/topics/action-games?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+myapp+%28ID%3A+285523%29","followersCount":3451,"postsCount":1254},{"id":"143","slug":"horror-games","name":"Horror Games","description":"DO NOT go in there. Okay, do it and then tell us what happens. 🙈 ","image":null,"url":"https://www.producthunt.com/topics/horror-games?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+myapp+%28ID%3A+285523%29","followersCount":1696,"postsCount":90},{"id":"142","slug":"platformers","name":"Platformers","description":"Platformers have been around for a long time in video games and for good reason. Jump around through the colorful world of Mario to the unforgiving dangers in Super Meat Boy.","image":null,"url":"https://www.producthunt.com/topics/platformers?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+myapp+%28ID%3A+285523%29","followersCount":2150,"postsCount":377},{"id":"141","slug":"driving-games","name":"Driving Games","description":"We all love to drive fast. The police aren't big fan of it. If you want to become Ricky Bobby for an afternoon, get behind the wheel of these speedsters.","image":"https://ph-files.imgix.net/001f9898-299a-4735-a12c-65d879f1e211.png?auto=format","url":"https://www.producthunt.com/topics/driving-games?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+myapp+%28ID%3A+285523%29","followersCount":1514,"postsCount":170},{"id":"140","slug":"rpgs","name":"RPGs","description":"You've got a ne